'''利奧波德咖啡館'''，是一間在[[印度|印度]][[孟買|孟買]]的[[餐廳|餐廳]]，在[[警局|警局]]對面<ref>{{cite news |last1=Fuller |first1=Thomas |title=Boozy and Raucous, a Cafe Defies Terror |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2008/12/15/world/asia/15mumbai.html |accessdate=2021-08-29 |work=The New York Times |date=2008-12-15 |archive-date=2021-08-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210829120854/https://www.nytimes.com/2008/12/15/world/asia/15mumbai.html }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last1=Vazquez |first1=Tatiana |title=Microsoft 365 'Life' se lanzará en la primavera de 2020con Office, administrador de contraseñas y más - HYPERNOIR |url=http://www.blonnet.com/life/2004/12/24/stories/2004122400130300.htm |accessdate=2021-08-29 |work=hypernoir.com |language=es-MX |archive-date=2008-12-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081202161312/http://www.blonnet.com/life/2004/12/24/stories/2004122400130300.htm }}</ref>。这間咖啡馆整天有[[外国人|外国人]]光顧，因為在2003年，有位暢銷[[澳洲|澳洲]]的[[作家|作家]][[格里高利·大卫·罗伯兹|格里高利·罗伯兹]]（{{lang|en|Gregory David Roberts}}）在其[[自傳|自傳]][[小說|小說]]《[[項塔蘭|項塔蘭]]》（{{lang|en|Shantaram}}）中描寫過该咖啡室。 <ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.eslite.com/product.aspx?pgid=1002161601807993 |title=自傳式小說《Shantaram 項塔蘭》 |accessdate=2008-11-29 |archive-date=2016-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305134007/http://www.eslite.com/product.aspx?pgid=1002161601807993 |dead-url=no }}</ref>在這本書里，自傳式描寫一個富有[[傳奇|傳奇]]色彩的[[澳洲|澳洲]]囚犯，[[逃獄|逃獄]]和[[偷渡|偷渡]]去了印度，十年之後又被抓回澳洲重新服刑，在[[監獄|監獄]]寫小說。

2008年11月26日，利奧波德咖啡館發生舉世震驚的[[2008年孟買連環恐怖襲擊|恐怖襲擊]]<ref>{{cite news |title=Indian attacks: More than 80 reported dead as gunmen run amok in Mumbai |url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2008/nov/26/mumbai-terror-attacks-india |accessdate=2021-08-29 |work=the Guardian |date=2008-11-26 |language=en |archive-date=2013-09-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130904061517/http://www.theguardian.com/world/2008/nov/26/mumbai-terror-attacks-india }}</ref>。

